title: CCENT-CCNA Into - Packet Tracer app and lessons - videos
description:
Included here are the Packet Tracer lessons and labs from Cisco Net Academy - CCENT - Module 1.

If you sign up for the class, you get the online instruction, which includes a walk-through with slides and videos, even a large book, and we meet twice a week with an instructor, which of course aren't included here. (Ever try to compress a CCNA instructor?) This zip file is only the packet tracer apps, the packet tracer lessons and lab sheets from the website. If you are planning on earning your CCNA or just the CCENT, I encourage you to enroll in a class, in person or brick-and-mortar. However, if you're a badass, buy a book and read it and use these scenarios and lessons, you should be alright. Lot's of activities and lessons, even a subnetting worksheet and many subnetting videos.

This package is also useful/helpful for anyone interested in Network+, although I didn't include any Comptia Network+ books! Basically, everything I used for school and downloaded from other places is all here.

Directory of Folders:

CCNA R&S 1 Lab Activities
CCNA R&S 2 Lab Activities
Packet Tracer Activities & Labs
Cisco Class - CCNA Appendixes (From Website)
Misc Activities
PDFs
Videos (Many on Subnetting, since it's a bitch)
---------
Three Versions of the latest Packet Tracer as of 15 Apr 16:

PacketTracer63_linux.tar
PacketTracer63_setup
iTunes6464Setup
